WEBVTT

00:02:29.484 --> 00:02:33.710
which isn't surprising when you consider
that there are still nine countries

00:02:33.710 --> 00:02:36.234
where women can be killed for straying.

00:02:37.825 --> 00:02:42.420
Now, monogamy used to be
one person for life.

00:02:42.912 --> 00:02:45.515
Today, monogamy is one person at a time.

00:02:46.268 --> 00:02:48.133
(Laughter)

00:02:48.158 --> 00:02:50.023
(Applause)

00:02:52.364 --> 00:02:54.300
I mean, many of you probably have said,

00:02:54.300 --> 00:02:56.888
"I am monogamous in all my relationships."

00:02:57.460 --> 00:02:59.863
(Laughter)